OL,7,FItalian restaurant workers toiling in
OL,8,Fextreme temperatures say British
OL,9,Ftourists are notably absent this
OL,10,Fsummer, with one saying customers are
OL,11,Fsimply too hot to eat and drink much.
OL,13,FAdriana Deligios, a part-time
OL,14,Fwaitress at Il Mirto in Alghero,
OL,15,Fnorthwest Sardinia, said there had
OL,16,Fbeen fewer UK visitors this year
OL,17,F"especially in May and June".
OL,19,F"We've had a few lately, but this
OL,20,Fyear there are only a few Brits," the
OL,21,F32-year-old told i.
